metadata.name: The Queen of the Predatory Cake
metadata.description:
There is a cake on the table.
 It's so fresh, it smells like cream and strawberries. Droplets of thick white cream flow down from the rosy sponge cake. 

This cake is looking at me. It clearly wants something from me. 
Why is this predatory cake haunting me?

4000Ñ…4000 px
